  "description": "Cloud Core Router, 16x Gigabit Ethernet Ports, 2x 10G SFP+ Cages, RJ-45 Konsolenport, 4GB DDR4 RAM, 128MB NAND",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Consolidating Networks with CCR",
      "text": "MikroTik's Cloud Core Router series, introduced in early 2023, represents a cutting-edge lineup of high-capacity routers designed to connect and consolidate small computer networks into a single large network. These routers offer powerful single-core performance, making them ideal for handling heavy operations with per-connection processing. The series features a range of models with various port configurations and redundant power supplies, catering to diverse networking needs for businesses, ISPs, research facilities, and more. With their advanced features and affordability, MikroTik's Cloud Core Routers are a reliable choice for taking networking setups to the next level."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Powerful Networking Solution",
      "text": "Introducing the MikroTik CCR2004-16G-2S+PC router, a true powerhouse that combines cutting-edge performance with silent operation. Equipped with the Amazon Annapurna Labs Alpine v2 CPU, featuring 4x 64-bit ARMv8-A Cortex-A57 cores running at 1.2 GHz, this router delivers a staggering 3x speed increase compared to previous CCR models. Experience the full potential of a real CCR router without any noise disruptions, making it the perfect choice for offices, studios, server rooms, or home labs, all while ensuring top-notch performance."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Seamless Connectivity & Versatile Ports",
      "text": "The CCR2004-16G-2S+PC offers seamless networking with its 16x 1 Gbps Ethernet ports and two 10G SFP+ cages. This extensive port range allows you to effortlessly manage data-intensive tasks and experience lightning-fast data transfers over wired connections. Whether you're expanding your office network or handling a large-scale setup, the router's scalability ensures you can accommodate growing demands without a hitch."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Compact Design, Exceptional Reliability",
      "text": "Designed with efficiency in mind, the CCR2004-16G-2S+PC boasts a classic white 1U rackmount case, easily integrating into your network environment. Its rackmount and desktop mounting options offer flexible deployment, ensuring the router fits perfectly into your networking setup. With 4GB of DDR4 RAM and 128MB of storage memory, this router handles advanced configurations and updates with ease, ensuring your network operates smoothly and stably."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Enhanced Cooling & Redundant Power",
      "text": "No need to worry about overheating or unexpected downtime. The CCR2004-16G-2S+PC features efficient active cooling to maintain optimal temperatures during operation, ensuring consistent and reliable performance even under heavy workloads. Additionally, the built-in dual redundant power supplies offer added peace of mind, guaranteeing uninterrupted network connectivity for your critical operations."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Future-Ready SFP+ Ports",
      "text": "Embrace the future of networking with the two 10G SFP+ cages, delivering blazing-fast data transmission rates. These high-speed ports not only provide seamless connections but also prepare your network for upcoming technological advancements, making the CCR2004-16G-2S+PC a smart and future-proof investment."
    }
  ],
